for that, for somebody

00:50:24.480 --> 00:50:27.600
to leave work, you
know, little movies,

00:50:27.600 --> 00:50:28.670
and little things behind.

00:50:28.670 --> 00:50:30.000
So absolutely.

00:50:30.000 --> 00:50:32.230
You can't say that,
oh, there's not

00:50:32.230 --> 00:50:34.240
an opportunity, when
there's an opportunity

00:50:34.240 --> 00:50:36.400
at your fingertips every day.

00:50:36.400 --> 00:50:38.760
So yes, incredibly.

00:50:38.760 --> 00:50:42.640
