00:50:55.980 --> 00:50:57.396
So there's no
excuse to say, well,

00:50:57.396 --> 00:50:58.810
I don't know how to do that.

00:50:58.810 --> 00:51:00.950
Or I can't get
there and do that.

00:51:00.950 --> 00:51:02.820
You can go all over the world.

00:51:02.820 --> 00:51:03.769
There's no excuses.

00:51:03.769 --> 00:51:05.310
I always try to find
an excuse, but--

